\f[CR]\[at]page\f[R] rules loaded by the document.
.SS CSS
Below we define styles for the page using a \f[CR]\[at]page\f[R] rule.
.IP
.EX
\f[B]\[at]page\f[R] {
  \f[B]margin\f[R]: 1cm;
