.SS JavaScript
The code iterates through all the sheets in the document, and through
all the \f[CR]cssRules\f[R] in each sheet, logging the sheet index, the
number of rules, and the type of each rule object.
We then detect \f[CR]CSSPageRule\f[R] objects using their type (doing
nothing with the information).
